<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"></head>
<body style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">

  <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Dear <strong>{{receiver_name}}</strong>,</p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    My name is <strong>{{sender_from_name}}</strong>, and I serve as <strong>{{position}}</strong> at our organization.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    I came across your profile and was impressed by your work at <strong>{{company}}</strong>. I believe there may be an opportunity for us to collaborate and create mutual value.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Would you be open to a brief conversation sometime next week? I'd love to share more about what we're building and explore how we might work together.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Best regards,</p>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 2px;"><strong>{{sender_from_name}}</strong></p>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-top: 0;">{{position}}</p>

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 30px 0;">

  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
    If you'd prefer not to receive future messages, you can reply with "unsubscribe" and we'll honor your request.
  </p>

</body>
</html>
